Cool Astro Forms — Clean-Room Notice

This project is an independent, clean-room reimplementation of form-abandonment
capture, user-journey tracking, notification, payment, and file-storage
behaviors commonly found in WordPress form plugins and their addons.

No source code from WPForms, WPForms Pro, or any WPForms addon (GPL-licensed)
has been copied, translated, or otherwise incorporated into this repository.
All behavior in this project has been independently re-implemented in
TypeScript against publicly documented APIs (Astro, Node.js, better-sqlite3,
nodemailer, browser platform APIs) and original design decisions recorded in
this project's own planning documents.

Product and company names mentioned in this project's documentation (including
"WordPress" and "WPForms") are used only in a nominative, descriptive sense —
to describe the migration scenario this package addresses — and do not imply
any affiliation, sponsorship, or endorsement by their respective trademark
holders.

